{"tid":141281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致高登打手／五毛同埋最低賤既早洩","createTime":"2017-03-02T19:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T11:11:30.000Z","uid":17510,"like":75,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7299b1787dcb34586c2cc69a86b391f125735b71","tid":141281,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:09:49.000Z","msg":"估唔到早洩到今時今日都仲係咁不知悔改<br />\n向到縱容你班手下胡作非為<br />\n<br />\n我地黎得LIHKG<br />\n一早係將自己身家性命交託左比連巴<br />\n我地絕對相信連巴唔似得早洩咁卑鄙無恥<br />\n<br />\n老老實實  如果你肯一早為BAM HKG+而公開地躹躬道歉<br />\n根本就唔會搞到今時今日咁樣既局面<br />\n<br />\n到左今日高登再無高登仔係閣下咎由自取<br />\n你以為打殘LIHKG我地就會返返去你個垃圾高登只係你夢心妄想<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月出得第一個LIHKG  <br />\n我地就有本事可以再出得到千千萬萬個LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多都無謂<br />\n我地對連尼住同望遠兩位巴打係無條件信任<br />\n當中既情義係你依啲反覆無常既小人唔會明白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之一句到尾<br />\n我就點都撐LIHKG"},{"pid":"ad6575eb75ac39e4410c0249a9c304b013eecbe3","tid":141281,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:35:36.000Z","msg":"連巴加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望連登仔唔好咁無聊走去騷擾連巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efea691b6d180098386f5e6d36b2efbad1745a2d","tid":141281,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5a35a719ee57e90bb32ebd2bb3ee06a3b2a9a6","tid":141281,"uid":20619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:44:35.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"68c7256b8dc8999e821124adbfbba0cec266a412","tid":141281,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T20:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb9b5f1e0eadf2c80569fd08601470fe63d3fcb","tid":141281,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T20:46:12.000Z","msg":"老老實實，有無計宣傳高登到底有幾死寂？<br />\n直接打鳩爛早洩同班打手嘅飯碗唔好煩<img src=\"/